Description: SecuBox WireGuard VPN Dashboard
 WireGuard VPN management interface for SecuBox.
 Features:
  - Interface management (up/down/status)
  - Peer management with auto-config and QR codes
  - Traffic statistics and monitoring
  - Migration from OpenWrt
  - Three-fold architecture (Components/Status/Access)
